Function Documentation

static void CANFD_configMessageRAM ( const CANFD_DriverMCB *  ptrCanFdMCB,
const CANFD_MCANMsgRAMCfgParams *  configParams,
int32_t *  errCode 
)
static

Description
Function initializes the CANFD driver instance with the specified hardware attributes. It resets and configures the MCAN module, sets up the Message RAM and ECC Aggregator. It configures the CANFD driver with the control parameters.

Parameters
[in]ptrCanFdMCBPointer to the CANFD driver MCB
[in]configParamsCAN module configuration parameters
[out]errCodeError code populated on error
Return values
Success- Handle to the CAN Driver
Error- NULL
